===Alternative forms===
Note that in Taiwan and Hong Kong, the character is written with {{l-lite|mul|sc=Hani|卝}} on top instead of {{l-lite|mul|sc=Hani|艹}}, as found in the [[Kangxi]] dictionary. Traditionally, the character is listed under the radical {{l-lite|mul|sc=Hani|夕}} (sunset). However, in simplified Chinese and Japanese dictionaries, the character may be listed under the radical {{l-lite|mul|sc=Hani|艹}} (grass) as the {{l-lite|mul|sc=Hani|卝}} (crown/hairstyle) component has been simplified to {{l-lite|mul|sc=Hani|艹}}.

